  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "heading",
          "level": 2,
          "anchor": "Overview",
          "text": "Overview"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "When the system needs to retrieve one or more specific instances of an app",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "entity, it asks you to provide a relevant query type. The system uses queries",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " "
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "during parameter resolution when the parameter of an intent contains"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " "
            },
            {
              "text": "an entity. The system also uses them to resolve information in a different",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "format into one of your app’s entities. For example, it uses them to"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " "
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "resolve natural spoken language into one of your app’s entities."
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The system can sometimes determine which entities it needs and provide you"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " "
            },
            {
              "text": "with a list of corresponding identifiers. Provide an ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.AppIntents/documentation/AppIntents/EntityQuery"
            },
            {
              "text": " type",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "to supply the entities for those identifiers. Provide additional query"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "types to perform more advanced searches, such as a search that matches"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " "
            },
            {
              "text": "specific properties of the entity.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
